'''Islam''' yella d-ajjed (eddin) i deg ttamnen yinselmen belli [[Rebbi|Yakuc]] neɣ [[Rebbi]] d yiwen, ur yesɛi acrik. D Netta i d-ixelqen akk ameɣrad (''the universe''), ala Netta i yestahellen ad yettwaɛbed. 

Deg laxert, wid i yumnen s-yes, gan ayen i yefreḍ fell-asen ad aten-iger ɣer lǧennet, ma d wid ur yuminen s-yes, ɛsant ad aten-iger ɣer ǧahennama (times).Deg Lislam, Rebbi ixleq-d Lmalaykat seg tafat, Leǧnun seg tmes, amdan seg wakal. Yuzen imazanen (''les messagers'') ɣur medden akken ad amnen s yes ad rnun ad at-ɛebden s wayen isen-id icareɛ d wayen id-asen d-mlen imazanen-is. Deg Lislam amazan (Rrasul) aneggaru i d-iceggaɛ Rebbi d [[Muḥemmed]].

Isem n yemdanen i yettamnen s Lislam, [[Inselmen]]. Inselmen ɣur-sen 5 n tamara (lefroḍ):

* [[Ecchada]].
* [[Taẓallit]].
* [[Ezzakat]].
* [[Remḍan]].
* [[Elḥeǧǧ]].

Deg Lislam, yella yiwen wedlis : [[Leqran]]: D adlis id yessuder Rebbi ɣef umazan Muḥemmed. Yella daɣen [[Lḥadit]]: D imeslayen, igiten, neɣ ayen ɣef i yessusem (Aprobations)[[Muḥemmed]]. Inselmen ttamnen belli [[Abenǧil|Injil]] d [[Turat]] ttubeddlen, wer qqimmen amek i ten-id yuzen Rebbi.

